channel.title: Cant run any 718 clients
channel.description:
Anytime i download a 718 client i always get a threat pop up and for some reason AVG thinks that Class52_Sub2_Sub1_Sub1.class ia a virus. Any help would be great, thank you.
Also for some reason when i downloaded this client (http://www.rune-server.org/runescape-development/rs-503-client-server/downloads/448758-718-client-run-compiler-no-errors.html) it also tells me i don't have permission to copy the Class52_Sub2_Sub1_Sub1.class file which is weird.
Thanks again.
FIXED IT THANK YOU
turns out i just needed to turn off my antivirus while extracting and it works fine now.
